data.description:
A very, nice large condo located at The quiet Villas of Orlando community. A clean 1BR/1BA is located on the se one floor and includes a full sized Washer & Dryer. Recently renovated has tile flooring throughout. This apartment has your private dedicated, resident parking.
Lease rental rate also includes basic cable, water and trash.
The Villas of Orlando is a quite community only minutes to the Hourglass District and downtown. Restaurants and walking and bicycle trails. Publix only 6 blocks away, 1 block to Lake Underhill Park.

Application fee $100.00 (non refundable). per person
